Package: F2Adonis2
Title: Robust PERMANOVA using the F2 Statistic
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Lakviru", "Perera", email = "email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the robust F2 statistic and bias-adjusted 
    bootstrap for dissimilarity-based multivariate analysis of variance. 
    Based on the solutions for the multivariate Behrens-Fisher problem 
    proposed by Anderson et al. (2017) <doi:10.1111/anzs.12176>.
